<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 15:15:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国担心中国使用人工智能，称这可能使国家容易受到胁迫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-concerned-about-chinas-use-ai-says-it-could-make-countries-vulnerable-2024-10-24/</link><description>白宫国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文周四表示，美国政府对中国利用人工智能镇压本国人民、传播错误信息并破坏美国及其盟国的安全感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 14:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-concerned-about-chinas-use-ai-says-it-could-make-countries-vulnerable-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯提议的金砖国家粮食交易所可能需要数年时间才能启动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-proposed-grain-exchange-brics-countries-may-take-years-launch-2024-10-24/</link><description>俄罗斯关于建立新的国际粮食交易所的提议可能需要数年时间才能落实，尽管该计划在本周于俄罗斯喀山举行的峰会上受到金砖国家集团成员的欢迎。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 14:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-proposed-grain-exchange-brics-countries-may-take-years-launch-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>金砖国家峰会发生了什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/main-takeaways-brics-summit-2024-10-24/</link><description>以下是金砖国家领导人会晤成果的简要概述：</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 14:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/main-takeaways-brics-summit-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>全球食品巨头加大降价力度以吸引中国谨慎的购物者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/global-food-giants-deepen-price-cuts-tempt-chinas-wary-shoppers-2024-10-24/</link><description>高管们表示，达能和雀巢等国际公司已经加大了降价力度，或者正在寻求提高网上购物量，以赢得中国日益不愿购买的顾客。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 13:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/global-food-giants-deepen-price-cuts-tempt-chinas-wary-shoppers-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>金砖国家与西方燃料联盟同仇敌忾，步伐加快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/spurred-by-shared-grievances-brics-gathers-pace-2024-10-24/</link><description>本周在华盛顿举行的全球金融首脑会议笼罩着美国大选的紧张情绪，而弗拉基米尔·普京则在俄罗斯城市喀山欢迎各国领导人，这些国家的人口加起来接近世界人口的一半。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 13:07:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/spurred-by-shared-grievances-brics-gathers-pace-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>对金砖国家领导人首次扩大峰会的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/reactions-first-expanded-brics-summit-2024-10-24/</link><description>俄罗斯本周主办了新扩大的新兴经济体金砖国家俱乐部的首次峰会，领导人就从粮食交换到跨境支付系统等一系列共同项目达成了一致。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 12:15:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/reactions-first-expanded-brics-summit-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>德国部长称农业是印度与欧盟自由贸易谈判中“问题最严重”的领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/agriculture-most-problematic-area-india-eu-trade-pact-talks-german-minister-says-2024-10-24/</link><description>德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克周四表示，在印度与欧盟之间达成自由贸易协定的谈判中，农业是“问题最大”的领域，他建议最好首先关注工业部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 12:11:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/agriculture-most-problematic-area-india-eu-trade-pact-talks-german-minister-says-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>普京警告中东战火并在金砖国家讨论乌克兰问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-warns-middle-east-conflagration-debates-ukraine-brics-2024-10-24/</link><description>俄罗斯、中国和印度呼吁在中东建立两国解决方案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 12:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-warns-middle-east-conflagration-debates-ukraine-brics-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：巴基斯坦向国际货币基金组织申请 10 亿美元气候现金并预计储备将增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-formally-requests-imf-rst-money-targeting-1-bln-finance-minister-says-2024-10-24/</link><description>巴基斯坦财政部长告诉路透社，巴基斯坦向国际货币基金组织正式申请提供约 10 亿美元资金，以帮助中低收入国家减轻气候风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 11:52:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-formally-requests-imf-rst-money-targeting-1-bln-finance-minister-says-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>联合国秘书长呼吁加沙、黎巴嫩、乌克兰和苏丹实现和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/un-chief-calls-peace-gaza-lebanon-ukraine-sudan-2024-10-24/</link><description>联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯周四对包括俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在内的金砖国家领导人表示，世界需要加沙、黎巴嫩、乌克兰和苏丹的和平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 11:30:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/un-chief-calls-peace-gaza-lebanon-ukraine-sudan-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>原料巨头凯爱瑞认为美国大选和中国贸易紧张局势不会带来风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ingredients-giant-kerry-sees-no-risk-us-election-china-trade-tension-2024-10-24/</link><description>爱尔兰食品配料跨国公司凯里集团首席执行官埃德蒙·斯坎伦周四在接受采访时表示，公司认为即将到来的美国大选或与中国的贸易紧张局势不会对其业务构成重大风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 11:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ingredients-giant-kerry-sees-no-risk-us-election-china-trade-tension-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将与中国一起访问前线岛屿庆祝战斗周年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-visit-frontline-islands-with-china-battle-anniversary-2024-10-24/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德将于周五访问中国沿海的一组敏感前线岛屿，庆祝对共产党军队取得重大胜利 75 周年，此时距中国举行军演仅一周多时间。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-visit-frontline-islands-with-china-battle-anniversary-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着特斯拉飙升、收益率回落，市场反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-10-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 10:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>普京称中东正处于全面战争边缘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-says-middle-east-is-brink-full-scale-war-2024-10-24/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周四表示，随着以色列和伊朗之间的紧张局势急剧升级，中东正处于全面战争的边缘。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 08:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-says-middle-east-is-brink-full-scale-war-2024-10-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：欧洲机构表示正在与 SpaceX 就解决太空垃圾问题进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/europe-agency-says-it-is-talks-with-spacex-tackling-space-junk-2024-10-24/</link><description>欧洲航天局总干事约瑟夫·阿施巴赫 (Josef Aschbacher) 告诉路透社，欧洲航天局正在与 SpaceX 就埃隆·马斯克的航天事业加入旨在减少太空中不断增加的碎片的国际宪章的可能性进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 08:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/europe-agency-says-it-is-talks-with-spacex-tackling-space-junk-2024-10-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>